Description:
You come to a large owl statue that the elves use to protect the forest from the cold, but it seems to be malfunctioning. As you approach, you see a young elf who says to you:

"What are you doing in this forest? You shouldn't be here... the magic stone that powers this owl guardian is almost depleted. When its energy runs out, the cold will grow and the dead will advance into the sanctuary.

As an elf, it is my duty to stay and protect the sanctuary... If only I had another magic stone or something to replace it!
DescriptionAction: I'm sorry, but you must leave before it's too late."
